{"tid":2259080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國左派同右派遊行比較，如果你係美國人，你會支持邊班人？","createTime":"2020-10-26T13:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T14:47:46.000Z","uid":123264,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3eefc6773e446e76478c2e80270dad853bb35bde","tid":2259080,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y__yIlagOYg&amp;ab_channel=TheNewsJunkie%27sCartoons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy__yIlagOYg%26ab_channel%3DTheNewsJunkie%2527sCartoons&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=f28c77e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y__yIlagOYg&amp;ab_channel=TheNewsJunkie%27sCartoons</a><br />\n<br />\n美國Beverly Hills遊行，整到好似嘉年華咁，大家都好開心，洋溢節日氣氛，唔講仲以為係主題公園遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到好多人素不相識 但係互相握手影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似成個大家庭咁 我香港人都好想去睇下<br />\n<br />\n相反BLM遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRi-3ReSTMs&amp;ab_channel=BreitbartNews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkRi-3ReSTMs%26ab_channel%3DBreitbartNews&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=504968f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRi-3ReSTMs&amp;ab_channel=BreitbartNews</a><br />\n<br />\n走入去餐廳屌人老母? 點解? 因為佢地食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係煩撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e977c94136f8b6eb4c4f8d3487453fdd05d45bed","tid":2259080,"uid":370061,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"食嘢有咩問題？咁都屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6133297ff7eeab0aec354edc8d073b2ee0e20649","tid":2259080,"uid":123264,"like":5,"dislik